  <T n="name">0xF5789517<!--String: "Shoe Removal Sign"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP10\UI\Lessons\EP10_ShoeRemovalSign_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:48bd8e8610a379ac</T>
      <T n="text">0x1E43E8E8<!--String: "Take control of your household footwear. Place the new 'Taming of the Shoe' sign in your home to set rules about indoor approved footwear. Then just beware those mischievous sims who choose to break rules.\n**Also works with Men's and Women's Shoe racks. **"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP10\UI\Lessons\EP10_ShoeRemovalSign_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:48bd8e8610a379af</T>
      <T n="text">0xC50C3129<!--String: "You can set your household to have any of these rules.\n\nRemove Shoes Indoors: Sims will take off shoes when entering a household.\n\nAllow Shoes Indoors: Sims will wear whatever footwear they choose.\n\nWear Slippers Indoors: Sims will swap into slippers while indoors."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP10\UI\Lessons\EP10_ShoeRemovalSign_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:48bd8e8610a379ae</T>
      <T n="text">0x361A4172<!--String: "By default, when you place the 'Taming of the Shoe' sign in a household it will automatically set the rule to 'Remove Shoes Indoors' unless another sign is already placed with a rule already set.\n\nThe Men's and Women's shoe racks will not automatically set the 'Remove Shoes Indoors' rule."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
